In order to avoid port collision, please use two computers to test.

please input your user name upon start
In the left up corner, there is a menu button in which there are "connect" and "create room" button.
Please find your IP address in the log window. 
When you click connect, you will be prompted to enter IP address of your desired destination.
When you create room, you need to provide a room name.

Interaction:
1. send message
		click send button to send message
2. send image (unknown type)  
		it might take a while to send an image.
3. leave room   
		when someone left the chatroom, there will be a broadcast message like "xxx left the room" 
4. join room 
		when someone join the chatroom, there will be a broadcast message like "xxx join the room"